title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 3 2022
description:
C&B nerd out on the latest election data. Kari Lake's masterclass answer for a grieving mom used in ad against her. John Fetterman has a future as an ESPN football analyst. Kelly Tshibaka joins Clay and Buck to discuss her fight against Murkowski and McConnell for Alaska parents. Don Bolduc attacked, media and Democrats silent.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
